Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想再體會一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為喜歡的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是來抽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇妙的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在夢中忘記了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷今天休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學她？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又跑哪去偷懶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼  你都要守護好鈴君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  杉並同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很  很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那樣注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回過神來就已經在注視著直枝君了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過卻總是在意周圍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法把心意傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣  是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  明明直枝君已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  她說我喜歡的人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜歡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會浮現出鈴的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  不對  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理所當然的一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來  我在慌張什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是被告白而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  理樹你被告白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上個月鈴也被三年級的告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說希望能跟她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴不懂什麼是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心煩意亂  於是我幫她拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有這麼個事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在慌什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可  可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有了男朋友也毫不意外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴居然也會有被人告白的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛被嚇成這樣  真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想什麼虧心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不虧心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來  今天有貓罐頭的半價促銷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西可重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買得真划算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪們一定會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹也幫了不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴小時候經常被錯認為男孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是被三年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話把我嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不可能永遠當小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴和別人交往也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換成我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  你也被別人告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介說的  理樹在煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  這樣問題就都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是喜歡沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  來交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉並同學所說的一定是鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  最後怎麼變成了我跟鈴交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  我喜歡鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  大家是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.54,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz18.97\pos(240,263)}理樹、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.54,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz18.97\pos(296,274)}你還好嗎？（∵）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.43,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(231,245)\frz46.65\1c&HBD85EE&}我很好哦 {\fnsimhei\fs20}(*^_^*)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.14,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz2.7\pos(283,172)\fs28}其實也沒什麼事（∵）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次收到閒聊的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去告訴大家  首先是恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然由我這個男生說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過先提出的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要看誰先提出啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事不由男生來說的話就沒立場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟恭介說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像請求父親大人把女兒嫁給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭  恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道有事  究竟是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  看起來烏雲密佈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  感覺要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交到女朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是  挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  對象是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是鈴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你總是這樣無所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們終於察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太親密反而難以察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期望你們能快點走到這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你們要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後要相互扶持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是在我離開這裡之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是恭介  離畢業還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多守護一會兒我和鈴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  跟理樹君？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就覺得遲早會變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後要在一起了啊  理樹君和小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小鈴幸福的話  我也會幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們總算走到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們很相配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到好事當然得笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢  其實我們還沒什麼實感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家今後也能像往常一樣對待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦  我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個  開始交往了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉…嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道真人喜歡鈴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不就沒法和理樹玩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我就是想跟理樹在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  我的房間也要被鈴換走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們忍心讓我寂寞地一個人住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你依舊可以跟理樹一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房間也不用換哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  這才是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來小葉子也放下心來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入Little Busters之後  雖然有過不少幸福的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天這格外幸福的感覺我一定不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來你倆  為什麼不坐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要非坐在對角線兩端不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託  別總拿我們開涮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢  接過吻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越來越像個女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是變得越來越狂野了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  別戲弄我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些  趕緊去找鈴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有些害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那我們是為什麼而交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那你留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同於以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴已經是我的女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  世界彷彿變了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是叫了你一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別突然叫我啊  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要跟我吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的對話是不是有些詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不像是戀人間的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如你現在的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和現在的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列儂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  上面有信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個課題又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們最後的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在班會上參加競選
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.47,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,600)\K120}這個世界裡存在著秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密終於要揭曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份羈絆將受到考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  最後的課題
